files.name: .editorconfig
files.content:
root = true

# Reflects the current formatting of code in repo
# while we are actively discussing tabs vs spaces

# Unix-style newlines with a newline ending every file
[*]
end_of_line = lf
insert_final_newline = true

[*.imba]
charset = utf-8
indent_style = tab
indent_size = 4

[*.js]
charset = utf-8
indent_style = tab
indent_size = 4

[package.json]
indent_style = space
indent_size = 2
